author: The Q
description:
Smart Girl Shows How to Build Candy Dispenser | The Q

This is second episode of The Q Girls!

In this video you could learn how to make amazing candy dispenser. You need some cardboard, popsicle sticks, spring, acrylic glass and of course a lot of candys! You can used M&M's, Skittles, Nerds, Tic Tac and any other small candys. This is family friendly machine that will impress everyone :)

If you like this video don't forget to subscribe :)
